name: CoindefixDAO
description:
CoindefixDAO is a group of talented cypherpunks who have years of experience in the field of 

Business analysis,

The DAO is raising funds in regards to uniting crypto-essence under one informational hub.

information to better engage and maintain new users, which will further allow us to attract new business partners.

1. Paid services, not limited to market analytics, crypto consultations, education, market sentiment and signals
2. Digital space for top tier advertisements / NFTs / News / Partnership
